{{wikipedia|Slate (disambiguation)}}

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|esclate|lang=fro}}, from {{term|esclat|lang=fro}} (French {{term|éclat|lang=fr}}).

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/sleɪt/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|eɪt|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} A fine-grained homogeneous [[sedimentary]] [[rock]] composed of [[clay]] or [[volcanic]] [[ash]] which has been [[metamorphose]]d so that it [[cleave]]s easily into thin [[layer]]s.
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} The [[bluish]]-[[grey]] [[colour]] of most slate.
#: {{color panel|708090}}
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A sheet of slate for writing on with [[chalk]].
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A tile made of slate.
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A record of [[money]] owed.
#: ''Put it on my '''slate''' – I’ll pay you next week.''
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A list of affiliated [[candidate]]s for an [[election]].
#: ''Roy Disney led the alternative '''slate''' of directors for the stockholder vote.''
# An [[artificial]] material resembling slate and used for the same purposes.
# A thin plate of any material; a flake.

